msgstr ""
"Gott sei Dank! Gawen, wie fühlst du dich? Kannst du sprechen, dich bewegen?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/01_Breaking_the_Circle.cfg:497
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I feel weak... sick... (pause) ... I can't remember anything... nothing. "
