msgid ""
"I feel weak... sick... (<i>pause</i>) ...I can't remember anything... "
"nothing. Who am I?"
msgstr ""
"Ich fühle mich schwach... krank... (Pause) ... Ich kann mich an nichts "
"erinnern... nichts. Wer bin ich?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/01_Breaking_the_Circle.cfg:498
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
